gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地<span style=\"color: red;\">只要人,<strong>一齊趕絕休息撚 付諸行動 自己香港要自己救<br />\n<br />\n不要將抗爭外判 不要愧對義士 不要令自己後悔</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1ERLcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1ERLcz.jpg&h=1ea16afc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58cc67af9d262c2ac261c4e2a1e669d75863a48b","tid":1644940,"uid":256786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T22:37:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b210f06858216cd050cadf825417dd828a3318b","tid":1644940,"uid":278399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T23:06:38.000Z","msg":"哩單嘢推極都推唔起<br />\n香港人未唞夠？"},{"pid":"aee8681092e4df74186e7a32fb5597a8853d191d","tid":1644940,"uid":324198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:38:19.000Z","msg":"由尋日開始推唔到上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5909133df69c1618b6bfb0f1c2343f85619832","tid":1644940,"uid":13277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:07:56.000Z","msg":"行動post 無人推！！"}]}